Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: CBRE Limited (“CBRE”) has been retained as the exclusive sales representative for the sale of ±0.87 ac development land located on Principale-Ouest Avenue in Dieppe, New Brunswick. Conveniently woven into the desirable Dieppe community, this site represents an exceptional multifamily development opportunity in a growing submarket. The property is just steps from a GoodLife, Aquatic Centre, among others. Additionally, Jean Coutu, Dollarama, and Coop IGA is less than one block from the property, making grocery shopping a breeze for future tenants.The asset provides quick access to other parts of Greater Moncton due to convenient Champlain and Highway 15 access. The site is within close proximity to multiple Transit Bus lines, providing easy access to public transportation.
